OL,4,C'accidental', inquest rules
OL,6,FA boy who was fascinated with fire
OL,7,F"accidentally" started a house blaze
OL,8,Fwhich killed him and another one of
OL,9,Fhis family members, an inquest has
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FRiley Chambers, 9, and Siobhan Abbott,
OL,13,F24 died as a result of their injuries,
OL,15,FThe incident happened on Rawson Street
OL,16,Fin Selston in the early hours on
OL,17,FSunday morning on January 14 earlier
OL,18,Fthis year.
