OL,4,C'accidental', inquest rules
OL,6,FNottingham Coroner's Court heard that
OL,7,FRiley was a "poor sleeper" who would
OL,8,Fwake in the night. He had been put to
OL,9,Fbed at around 7:30pm on January 13 in
OL,10,Fan upstairs bedroom in the normal
OL,11,Fpattern.
OL,13,FCCTV from the front of the property
OL,14,Fshowed a series of small flashes
OL,15,Fbefore a smoke alarm was heard going
OL,16,Foff shortly before 1am.
OL,18,FRiley's family were then woken up to
OL,19,Fthe sound of the smoke alarm and his
OL,20,Fparents and sister managed to escape
OL,21,Fthe blaze through the kitchen.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
