OL,4,C'accidental', inquest rules
OL,6,FFire crews arrived and found Riley and
OL,7,FSiobhan in different rooms in the
OL,8,Fhouse.
OL,10,FThe inquest was told the fire started
OL,11,Fas a result of a "naked flame" coming
OL,12,Finto contact with combustible
OL,13,Fmaterials.
OL,15,FFour lighters were recovered from the
OL,16,Fhouse, two of which were in a cupboard
OL,17,Fin Riley's bedroom.
