OL,4,C'accidental', inquest rules
OL,6,FSiobhan died on January 16 at
OL,7,FNottingham City Hospital and Riley
OL,8,FChambers died two days later at the
OL,9,FQueen's Medical Centre.
OL,11,FA joint investigation by
OL,12,FNottinghamshire Fire and Rescue
OL,13,FService and Nottinghamshire Police
OL,14,Ffound there was no suspicious
OL,15,Fcircumstances and no evidence of third
OL,16,Fparty involvement in the fire.
