OL,4,C'accidental', inquest rules
OL,6,FAssistant coroner Nathanael Harley
OL,7,Fsaid: "Having heard all the evidence
OL,8,Fand relying upon extensive
OL,9,Finvestigations carried out by the
OL,10,Fpolice and fire service, I find Riley
OL,11,Fstarted a small fire in the hallway.
OL,13,F"Sadly, that fire spread, resulting in
OL,14,Fsignificant fire to the property,
OL,15,Fleading to his and Siobhan's death. I
OL,16,Fhave considered whether Siobhan's
OL,17,Fdeath ought to be concluded as an
OL,18,Funlawful killing.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
