OL,4,C'accidental', inquest rules
OL,6,F"However, I'm aware of Riley's
OL,7,Fneurodiversity and, crucially, his
OL,8,Fage, and consider the most appropriate
OL,9,Fconclusion to be an accidental death
OL,10,Ffor Siobhan."
OL,12,F"Riley's death was also concluded as
OL,13,Faccidental for the same reasons,
OL,14,Frather than misadventure."
