OL,4,C'accidental', inquest rules
OL,6,FChris Navin, station manager and fire
OL,7,Finvestigator of the incident, said:
OL,8,F"Following thorough investigations by
OL,9,Fourselves and our colleagues at
OL,10,FNottinghamshire Police, and following
OL,11,Fthe inquest today, the most probable
OL,12,Fcause of this tragic incident has been
OL,13,Fdeemed as a naked flame combined with
OL,14,Fcombustible materials.
OL,16,F"This is an extremely sad incident,
OL,17,Fand we would like to send our sincere
OL,18,Fcondolences to the family and friends
OL,19,Fof both Riley and his aunt, Siobhan."
